{"tid":1808069,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"招手足一齊整野係年宵義賣，金主比成本，不扣成本全捐 (已有攤檔)","createTime":"2020-01-02T06:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T12:32:42.000Z","uid":126397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0a4ad067d23c5cd9807f999bed9614c1d2f2027c","tid":1808069,"uid":126397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:40:50.000Z","msg":"換1換acc同小量update先<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1785345/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1785345/page/1</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1799759/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1799759/page/1</a><br />\n是咁的，由6月以來，已經有超過6000位手足被捕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n臨近農曆新年，我同一班手足諗住喺今年年宵做返啲嘢希望可以支援到哩班手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家一星期會有幾日開放手工制品工作坊 (可自選時段，詳情PM)<br />\n(唔分男女，咩類型手作都有，有專人教，步驟唔會太複雜，有耐性唔厭煩就得)<br />\n呢啲手作之後會放去年宵度義賣 (詳情呢度唔講太多，tg再傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n名額: 暫時搵住30位手足義務幫手先<br />\n被捕手足、俾屋企斷水斷糧手足、中學生手足優先<br />\n有金主可以提供交通同食飯津貼<br />\n所有收入會不扣除成本, 全數捐去支援前線手足嘅組織<br />\n如果你身邊識有朋友有類似嘅情況，可以幫手send呢個post畀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣可以tg我:<a href=\"https://t.me/smallanan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsmallanan&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPopBSCas1SUWCM4mOsPk5ns%3D&h=f92fec1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/smallanan</a> (睇到之後會盡快覆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\n問: 係咪請免費勞工?<br />\n答: 我哋都係一班後生仔女，大家都係無私咁貢獻自己嘅時間，無諗過賺錢。同埋你嚟到，就當你係手足咁看待<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問: 係咪食人血饅頭，消費緊場運動?<br />\n嚴格嚟講係，但香港抗爭就係一回咁諷刺嘅事，必然有好多同路人淨係畀錢當支持，亦有人花幾十萬去買民主女神像......年宵係勢在必行嘅活動，我哋嘅出現只係令到啲錢可以落到去最需要嘅手足身上<br />\n<br />\n問: 驚唔驚有鬼?<br />\n答: 我哋同大家一樣驚，但會盡量fact check，慢慢熟絡咗就會好啲，同埋都係整手作啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問︰點知你係唔係鬼?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nwvLe6s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnwvLe6s.png&h=f7fd5390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有即將上任既區議員鍾禮謙證實左我地既身份"},{"pid":"ca6d72441aa466878e0d9e986eec3a357c1bd06d","tid":1808069,"uid":126397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e7bcd09c305d0a8eb4e075ab0f702d8d965e30","tid":1808069,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:09:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[隨筆新詩]黎明前 光復後<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789990</a>"},{"pid":"ab218add2bdecf6a65f3d11c0c1148f8ea96bc61","tid":1808069,"uid":126397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42e7bcd09c305d0a8eb4e075ab0f702d8d965e30","tid":1808069,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:09:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[隨筆新詩]黎明前 光復後<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789990</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:20:46.000Z","msg":"thx大大"},{"pid":"d22824f8f7326d71ef9e9b52ce96d611c5eeb37d","tid":1808069,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be93fb123676f656e63971ec41a0efa74353b101","tid":1808